videos.description: Oregon State's Ethan Thompson throws the lob up to a wide-open Kylor Kelley for the two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Kelley sneaks behind the defense for alley-oop slam) 2020/3/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kelley sneaks behind the defense for alley-oop slam

videos.description: Ethan Thompson blows by Utah's defense for the emphatic slam.

videos.headline: Thompson drives baseline for the jam

videos.description: Alfonso Plummer nails his fifth 3-pointer to put Utah ahead of Oregon State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Plummer knocks down his 5th 3-pointer of the first half for Utah) 2020/3/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Plummer knocks down his 5th 3-pointer of the first half for Utah

videos.description: Alfonso Plummer breaks the Pac-12 tournament 3-point record with nine made 3-pointers, a record previously held by Warriors' star Klay Thompson.
